<plot>The story revolves around that timeless and controversial concept of power. The story is a powerful and graphic representation of power and its ability to corrupt.The story is a powerful rendition of our own secret fantasy of possessing power and being the harbinger of divine justice. The story is a moving description of our helplessness in the face of awareness of the illusion of power. The story is one that is told over and over again everywhere and yet is still waiting to be told.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?079390</url></doc>
